# This is the Hats Survey NPM package to all the About Repositories

# How to install
`npm install --save git+https://github.com/NetoRutes/hats-survey#v1.0.0`


## Edit in your gulp constants.js
### for closure
const hatsSurveyPath = 'node_modules/hats-survey/dist/closure/';

### for ts or js
const hatsSurveyPath = 'node_modules/hats-survey/dist/js/';


# How to contribute:
Edit the files `hats-survey` and `hats-survey-config`

## NODE + NPM versions
Node = v10.15.3
NPM = 6.4.1

## Install dependencies
`npm install`

## Build before publish
Before publish definitly you need to build the files 
to concat the imports, exports and 
closure modules declaration

`npm run build`
